{"tid":991051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港女權婦團無哂聲氣系列3】體壇MeToo　5名滑冰女選手指控教練性侵","createTime":"2019-01-22T05:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:28:55.000Z","uid":54337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ac8d5622b87c40a8132bdf43ccd8bbdda022e8","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"體壇MeToo　5名滑冰女選手指控教練性侵<br />\n01月21日(一) 20:00<br />\n<br />\n南韓短道速滑奧運金牌得主沈錫希，早前指控其教練趙宰範曾多次性侵及暴力對待，周一（21日）再有5名滑冰女運動員，聲稱曾遭教練性侵。<br />\n<br />\n組織「Solidarity for Young Skaters」在南韓國會開記招，表示再有女運動員被其男性教練性侵，但沒有公開當事人身份。議員孫惠園（Sohn Hye-won）稱，其中一名女事主青年時期在南韓國家體育大學（KNSU）就讀，當時多番遭教練撫摸、強吻及擁抱，她拒絕進一步接觸後曾被語言騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n孫惠園續指，滑冰界多次傳出性侵醜聞，但大部分涉事者未有受罰，因為涉事教練都是金明圭圈子的人，而受害人因為害怕遭到報復所以噤聲。現時在KNSU任教的金明圭是滑冰界名宿，他早前被指利用裙帶關係，在國際賽中重用KNSU出身的選手及教練；他亦涉嫌向受害者施壓，隱瞞對部分教練的性侵指控等。孫惠園已就事件，促請外界展開調查。"},{"pid":"cc3875f532e0612bc5834c2ce2ee37b21fbe2ab3","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190121/mobile/bkn-20190121200010052-0121_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190121%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190121200010052-0121_00912_001.html&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d1d40952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190121/mobile/bkn-20190121200010052-0121_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9660a09e2d85b7836599a53f95967ed2aff4a453","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:54:47.000Z","msg":"印度女人入神廟，你唔理<br />\n沙特少女逃婚，你唔理<br />\n南韓運動員被性侵犯，你又唔理。<br />\n<br />\n學Whitepy話齋，今次你地香港女權莫非又 &ldquo;忙到甩碌&rdquo;，&ldquo;人微言輕&rdquo;，&ldquo;世界好大，唔係每件事都可以關注到&rdquo; ？"},{"pid":"217ddb1c8d243cf2f302d8f1dd13fa7a4bd440c5","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"今次香港女權會唔會搞slut walk，遊行到南韓駐港領事館，大叫believe victim，聲援南韓女運動員呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185f6a54552951233bc9b8c34fe4498114aaabf9","tid":991051,"uid":128761,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"唔好話女權撚<br />\n連登班網絡狙擊手咪又係咁<br />\n無聊私人事就起人底貼人街招講左幾個月<br />\n真正社會不公就完全唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保撚、女權撚個d都係咁<br />\n飲筒就講足幾個月，佢地做緊其他唔環保既野就提都唔提<br />\n香港女仔受唔公平對待就講足幾年，對男仔不公既就見唔到<br />\n<br />\n唔難發現依d人全部都係現實既過街老鼠<br />\n冇能力搞大件事、唔會關心真正要關心既野<br />\n只係識自己係一角度打飛機圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702b5018b5d62cedcad02cd517cd3f1cd0cfde2e","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"香港女運動員呂麗瑤稱被教練性侵，香港女權就支持。<br />\n南韓女運動員被教練性侵犯，唔通南韓女運動員唔係女人咩？<br />\n香港女權呢？無理由無聲氣㗎？<br />\nslut walk呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb5190ee072e65e193011a59242423d001342d2","tid":991051,"uid":48874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"圖定老母"},{"pid":"2cf546486c71188b0e45042624bb766bec6b4481","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:21:03.000Z","msg":"【體壇#MeToo】韓選手性侵案越揭越多 再有5位冰上運動員投訴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190121/59166206\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59166206&d=hvi0Gj61P2aDcx%2Bz4nMIp%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=67bc17ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190121%2F59166206&h=33badb83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190121/59166206</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190121/large/1548043063_afb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190121%2Flarge%2F1548043063_afb7.jpg&h=931a7508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓體壇的性侵案越揭越多，繼奧運短道速滑金牌、滑冰好手沈錫希（Shim Suk-hee）月初表示曾遭國家隊教練性侵4年後，一個南韓運動員組織指，至少另有5位冰上運動員亦投訴過曾被教練性侵。<br />\n<br />\n關注年輕滑冰好手的組織「團結年輕選手」（Solidarity for Young Skaters）在南韓國會上表示表示，再發現多5位冰上運動員曾被教練性侵，但未透露她們的名字。其中一位在盛產國家隊代表、韓國體育大學就讀的女子表示，訓練時曾被教練不當撫摸，有時更會抱住她或親吻她，當她叫停對方時就會被辱罵。<br />\n<br />\n組織指南韓奧委會的管理層，應要為未能好好保護運動員而下台。<br />\n<br />\n#MeToo運動席捲南韓體育界，教練與運動員之間的「從屬」關係，以及當地的訓練文化一直受人唾罵。柔道、跆拳道和摔跤女運動員也曾指摘遭受過男教練性侵。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"d43e5a05d80d59806c9629e383f55f75aa01f17c","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:22:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/photo/bkn-20181202163028606-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181202183057\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181202163028606-1202_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181202183057&h=334946ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人呢？遊行示威呢？"},{"pid":"3eed4c19abbe43dbf989b030098f44cbd9a0d1e7","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YSkoirt_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYSkoirt_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=4f1cd709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人呢？去左邊？"},{"pid":"1f4bed607fda5b590e16d7142caf1493511a9400","tid":991051,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T06:25:22.0